c: 12
v: 51
t: "Ya ce: \"Mẽne ne babban al'amarinku, a lõkacin da kaka nẽmi Yũsufu daga kansa?\" Suka ce: \"Tsarki ga Allah yake! Ba mu san wani mummũnan aiki a kansaba.\" Mãtar Azĩz ta ce: \"Yanzu fagaskiya* ta bayyana. Nĩ ce nã nẽme shi daga kansa. Kuma lalle ne shĩ, haƙĩƙa, yanã daga mãsu gaskiya"